{
  "stem": "24212.1",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My name is Vera Laska.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what else?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "L-A-S-K-A.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My first name is Vera, V-E-R-A.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Oravec, O-R-A-V-E-C.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was born in 1928.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1st--21st of July.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, don't ask nasty questions.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Figure it out. 1928-- 78-- So I must be getting close to 70.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was born in Kosice, Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "K-O-S-I-C-E.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I grew up in a very interesting neighborhood, because it was an ethnic mixture, which gave me, now that I'm looking back, gave me some kind of a good background to what was to follow in my career in the United States, because my family at home spoke Czech.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The neighborhood was Slovak.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The school was Slovak, although there were many Czech teachers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was quite a bit of a minority among-- among us of Germans and Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Most kids.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, in that Central European milieu, most people spoke several languages, not like in the United States where we have a continent that speaks one language, English.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there, it's sort of mixed up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The countries are so small that if you start jogging, you jog out of your country.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You jog out of your language.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So by necessity you had to learn languages.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had-- in high school, we had several languages-- French, German, not mentioning Latin, which we had to take, which was very helpful in learning English later.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That is a very difficult question to answer because my mother came from a very well-to-do and highly respected family.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when she was young, there was lots of money to go around.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "While after she got married and divorced, there was no money.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So our home looked like a million dollars, with Persian rugs and what have you, but there was very little-- very little money.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
